u Only Live Twice","original_language":"en"},{"id":682,"adult":false,"title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","video":false,"overview":"Cool government operative James Bond searches for a stolen invention that can turn the sun's heat into a destructive weapon. He soon crosses paths with the menacing Francisco Scaramanga, a hitman so skilled he has a seven-figure working fee. Bond then joins forces with the swimsuit-clad Mary Goodnight, and together they track Scaramanga to a Thai tropical isle hideout where the killer-for-hire lures the slick spy into a deadly maze for a final duel.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":4.9709,"vote_count":2220,"poster_path":"/xVkbKwGnBVNQ122GN5bCTMyPbWz.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-04","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/3tpNEbRahT8smy7RraaWa0xg9Gv.jpg","original_title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","original_language":"en"},{"id":699,"adult":false,"title":"For Your Eyes Only","video":false,"overview":"A British spy ship has sunk and on board was a hi-tech encryption device. James Bond is sent to find the device that holds British launching instructions before the enemy Soviets get to it first.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.8858,"vote_count":2016,"poster_path":"/xV4Nnr6DjjERlqNikqDQX8LUgua.jpg","release_date":"1981-06-24","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/z7Jp7HAsY7MqXzPYzTjJnmOQk2r.jpg","original_title":"For Your Eyes Only","original_language":"en"},{"id":1979,"adult":false,"title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","video":false,"overview":"The Fantastic Four return to the big screen as a new and all powerful enemy threatens the Earth. The seemingly unstoppable 'Silver Surfer', but all is not what it seems and there are old and new enemies that pose a greater threat than the intrepid superheroes realize.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"popularity":5.4216,"vote_count":8291,"poster_path":"/1rxTraSO45jbvTrCeSvJ6RmOu1b.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-13","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/o2wYH40zW0JIYiYUTu6L4gsNy7E.jpg","original_title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","original_language":"en"},{"id":2001,"adult":false,"title":"We Own the Night","video":false,"overview":"A New York nightclub manager tries to save his brother and father from Russian mafia hitmen.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":2.6961,"vote_count":1468,"poster_path":"/fcb2c9BcRc21iiWih23FQfT39uB.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-12","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/fJWeJL39Pddz30ULiQBn4WIv5hx.jpg","original_title":"We Own the Night","original_language":"en"},{"id":2008,"adult":false,"title":"The Promise","video":false,"overview":"An orphaned girl, driven by poverty at such a young age, makes a promise with an enchantress. In return for beauty and the admiration of every man, she will never be with the man she loves. This spell cannot be broken unless the impossible happens: snow falling in spring and the dead coming back to life. Now a grown and beautiful princess, she regrets her promise, for all of the men she's loved has always been met with tragedy.","genre_ids":[14,18,28,53,10749],"popularity":1.9386,"vote_count":131,"poster_path":"/tdm4mlc27S1d72ub4Y4xcU2OlDD.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-15","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/AwlJ2bQGjfEuXLsL5XJAaxOmMuV.jpg","original_title":"无极","original_language":"zh"},{"id":2024,"adult":false,"title":"The Patriot","video":false,"overview":"After proving himself on the field of battle in the French and Indian War, Benjamin Martin wants nothing more to do with such things, preferring the simple life of a farmer. But when his son Gabriel enlists in the army to defend their new nation, America, against the British, Benjamin reluctantly returns to his old life to protect his son.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752,28],"popularity":5.8339,"vote_count":4214,"poster_path":"/fWZd815QxUCUcrWQZwUkAp9ljG.jpg","release_date":"2000-06-28","vote_average":7.183,"backdrop_path":"/jSHHUHRcShP6DJbg0H2lO4A8m9x.jpg","original_title":"The Patriot","original_language":"en"},{"id":2038,"adult":false,"title":"Iron Eagle III","video":false,"overview":"Chappy discovers a drug-smuggling scheme at his own air base. It turns out that the lives of some village people in Peru are at stake, and he decides to fly there with ancient airplanes and friends to free them.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.716,"vote_count":69,"poster_path":"/ylvfsnacoqsTdZuLty2XVRolnNH.jpg","release_date":"1992-01-09","vote_average":4.1,"backdrop_path":"/jHEFMgqEXGyHExaZ4w2gYkd34Uo.jpg","original_title":"Iron Eagle III","original_language":"en"},{"id":2061,"adult":false,"title":"Pusher","video":false,"overview":"A drug pusher grows increasingly desperate after a botched deal leaves him with a large debt to a ruthless drug lord.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"popularity":1.7252,"vote_count":831,"poster_path":"/9Myfvq4e2BySE5aosX8UzV9cUME.jpg","release_date":"1996-08-30","vote_average":6.993,"backdrop_path":"/fO8xmjkGsDBzyGdw6ZgwqVoK50w.jpg","original_title":"Pusher","original_language":"da"},{"id":1126738,"adult":false,"title":"HEIST","video":false,"overview":"In this fun thrilling action movie, a team of skilled criminals is hired by a private syndicate to steal a biological weapon that is being guarded by the military. The weapon has the potential to cause an apocalypse, and the team's mission is to prevent the military from using it. However, they soon find out that they have been betrayed by the syndicate's rogue agent, who has his own plans for the weapon. Will the team stop the agent and prevent the apocalypse?","genre_ids":[28,35,878,12],"popularity":0.2923,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/7HS4KcVFLw5EkztSsD2qfrAIact.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/pbUV0AJ1JubPSszoi0ZLrm7vKfZ.jpg","original_title":"HEIST","original_language":"ta"},{"id":929,"adult":false,"title":"Godzilla","video":false,"overview":"French nuclear tests irradiate an iguana into a giant monster that viciously attacks freighter ships in the Pacific Ocean. A team of experts, including Niko Tatopoulos, conclude that the oversized reptile is the culprit. Before long, the giant lizard is loose in Manhattan as the US military races to destroy the monster before it reproduces and it's spawn takes over the world.","genre_ids":[878,28,53],"popularity":5.4875,"vote_count":4144,"poster_path":"/xJVl1I95StraYAwaNbBkVoWE2qA.jpg","release_date":"1998-05-20","vote_average":5.65,"backdrop_path":"/gT4XVSEmGKOJ0EgSEUTfCeqgEtc.jpg","original_title":"Godzilla","original_language":"en"},{"id":975,"adult":false,"title":"Paths of Glory","video":false,"overview":"A commanding officer defends three scapegoats on trial for a failed offensive that occurred within the French Army in 1916.","genre_ids":[10752,18],"popularity":5.0908,"vote_count":3203,"poster_path":"/p7OHwomA8UOhe3EhckF2IetBTh9.jpg","release_date":"1957-10-25","vote_average":8.257,"backdrop_path":"/eTZkq5tI58Ec76AwPf1HOUoKtky.jpg","original_title":"Paths of Glory","original_language":"en"},{"id":979,"adult":false,"title":"Irreversible","video":false,"overview":"A woman’s lover and her ex-boyfriend take justice into their own hands after she becomes the victim of a rapist. Because some acts can’t be undone. Because man is an animal. Because the desire for vengeance is a natural impulse. Because most crimes remain unpunished.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":8.8872,"vote_count":3199,"poster_path":"/rxeDxo8FvZpLu6iplNpxdtAVnfu.jpg","release_date":"2002-05-22","vote_average":7.175,"backdrop_path":"/xV1EfNSEg6id6juJPr1vM6p9x5X.jpg","original_title":"Irréversible","original_language":"fr"},{"id":984,"adult":false,"title":"Dirty Harry","video":false,"overview":"When a madman dubbed 'Scorpio' terrorizes San Francisco, hard-nosed cop, Harry Callahan – famous for his take-no-prisoners approach to law enforcement – is tasked with hunting down the psychopath.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":4.0148,"vote_count":2668,"poster_path":"/scl2JDHzYoIEs5xyYy5ITCfyY0G.jpg","release_date":"1971-12-23","vote_average":7.446,"backdro